05T10:53:06.000Z","msg":"幫人權法再加辣，而且歐洲英國都焗住要跟隊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:15:28.000Z","msg":"如果禁互聯網，佢都唔知有咩影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n覺得佢出反蒙面已經幾嚇大<br />\n再敢唔敢出其他招真係睇林鄭月娥攬炒嘅決心有幾大<br />\n<br />\n而家佢有「權力」將香港擺上賭枱<br />\n呢個權力我地冇得唔「承認」嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d8e7e1ba3f700c01b3f2e31524e3dda2207ace0","tid":1626232,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9ace7df7b655f37c2ae248b6ec063e3f9f8ced4","tid":1626232,"uid":53254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:56:34.000Z","msg":"福建邦 白衣人 冇錢收唔見撚哂<br />\n定係飛天南扮俾人捉食夾棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:20:38.000Z","msg":"出得幾次已經好明顯<br />\n721 已經全世界望住<br />\n而家北角直頭變左福獨首都<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd9dfdb51bbebecbd2d4f263fab62716ba199ee3","tid":1626232,"uid":14449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:26:21.000Z","msg":"我呢家係同政府鬥大細<br />\n似乎政府有個masterplan <br />\n覺得認低威根本解決唔到問題<br />\n直接用唔同強硬手法<br />\n將反抗既一網打盡<br />\n順便重建成個社會<br />\n變到藍絲廢老理想既專權社會<br />\n然後政府認為先有效管治"},{"pid":"cad5d3cf70935fc4d3967ee8b2f0fd3fb7123a5a","tid":1626232,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd9dfdb51bbebecbd2d4f263fab62716ba199ee3","tid":1626232,"uid":14449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:26:21.000Z","msg":"我呢家係同政府鬥大細<br />\n似乎政府有個masterplan <br />\n覺得認低威根本解決唔到問題<br />\n直接用唔同強硬手法<br />\n將反抗既一網打盡<br />\n順便重建成個社會<br />\n變到藍絲廢老理想既專權社會<br />\n然後政府認為先有效管治"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:17:08.000Z","msg":"愈多人知道真相佢愈驚"},{"pid":"4d7bb45ad62fa34dcb481b8fcdafb2e04d504240","tid":1626232,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:52:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1d1255006aa5ab6cd75bb0b1cea9138d4bf672d5","tid"